openldap (40-0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Use Squeeze source: 2.4.23
  * Also use CVE security and other patches from Squeeze + SFW + structure.
  * debian/rules, debian/control:
    + Bring back slapd-dbg package.
    + Use dh_strip.
    + Do not use dh_testroot in install target. This fix non-root build.
  * debian/control:
    + Bring back slapd-dbg package.
    + Updated dependencies for slapd package.
    + Updated Build-Depends.
  * Added slapd SMF support using dh_installsvc.
  * Enable maintainer scripts for slapd.

